Download TIGER shapes for American Indian Tribal Subdivision National

Source: R/tribal_subdivisions.R
tt_tribal_subdivisions.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for American Indian Tribal Subdivision National

Usage

tt_tribal_subdivisions(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_tribal_subdivisions()
